import { GridItem, Heading, Center, SimpleGrid } from '@chakra-ui/layout'
import React from 'react'

import AspectCard from './AspectCard'
import AspectCardJalaine from './AspectCardJalaine'
import AspectCardMariela from './AspectCardMariela'
import AspectCardBruce from './AspectCardBruce'

function Homepage() {
  return (
    <GridItem colStart={{ md: 1, lg: 1 }} colSpan={{ md: 4, lg: 4 }}>
      {' '}
      <Center>
        {' '}
        <Heading> The Classical Maya </Heading>
      </Center>
      <SimpleGrid columns={{ sm: 2, md: 2, lg: 4 }} spacing={{ lg: 3 }}>
        <AspectCardJesse />
        <AspectCardJalaine />
        <AspectCardMariela />
        <AspectCardBruce />
      </SimpleGrid>
    </GridItem>
  )
}

export default Homepage
